<TITLE> JU summer vacation begins Wednesday </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Jahangirnagar University, May 12 (bdnews24.com)A month-long summer holiday at Jahangirnagar University is scheduled to begin Wednesday, a press release issued Tuesday said. All classes of all the departments will remain suspended during the vacation. The examinations, however, will be held as announced earlier. The university will return to business as usual on June 13. The JU offices will remain closed from May 16 to May 21. 
